# Project Overview

npm workspaces monorepo for a GitHub Action that parses test results (TRX/JUnit/NUnit/xUnit) and publishes reports via PR comments, job summaries, checks, and HTML artifacts.

## Repository map

- `src/` + `test/` — GitHub Action source and tests
- `web/` — React history dashboard (see `web/AGENTS.md`)
- `docs/` — Docusaurus site (see `docs/AGENTS.md`)
- `packages/` — Shared models and publisher (see `packages/AGENTS.md`)
- `dist/` — Bundled action (committed); rebuild after `src/` changes

Full navigation: [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md).

## Before finishing a task

```bash
npm test
npm run lint
npm run build    # required when src/ or action.yml changes
```

## Key rules

- `action.yml` is the source of truth for inputs — not README.
- Focused diffs only; no unrelated refactors.
- Parser/history changes need Vitest tests with fixtures.
- Update `docs/docs/` when changing user-facing behavior.
